ruby-odbc-0.2

This is an ODBC binding for Ruby. So far it has been tested with
MySQL 3.22, unixODBC 2.0.5, and Ruby 1.6.3 on Linux 2.2 for Intel.

Requirements:

    - Ruby 1.6.3
    - unixODBC 2.0.5

Installation:

    $ ruby extconf.rb
    $ make
    # make install

Usage:

    Refer to doc/odbc.html

